{
  "texts": [
    "Question type and logic group distribution are shown in Table 3.Of the 190 correct outputs, 179 provided a true consistent (CC) logic in answering the question (94.2%).",
    "Of the 170 incorrect outputs, 133 provided a true inconsistent (IIC) logic in answering the question (78.2%).A Chi-squared test was conducted to examine the associations between question topic, year administered, and whether the question was answered correctly.",
    "The test revealed a significant association with test topic and correct answer (χ 2 (10) = 23.020, p = 0.011).",
    "Post hoc analysis revealed that the Basic Science and Sports categories had adjusted residuals greater than 1.96, indicating a statistically significant departure from the expected frequencies.",
    "No significant association with test year and correct answer was observed (χ 2 (2) = 1.678, p = 0.432."
  ]
}